body:
Date: {{todayDate}}
To,
{{deptName}}
Subject: Submission of tender documents for {{tenderTitle}} ({{tenderId}})

Dear Sir/Madam,
We submit our tender documents for {{tenderTitle}}. All documents enclosed are authentic and complete to the best of our knowledge.

Authorized Signatory
{{contractorName}}
{{contactPerson}}

Subject: Declaration for submission of documents ({{tenderTitle}})

We hereby declare that the documents submitted are true copies of the originals. No bid amounts or rates are disclosed herein. We agree to comply with all tender terms.

Sincerely,
{{contractorName}}
{{contactPerson}}
{{contactMobile}}

We certify that {{contractorName}} has not been blacklisted or debarred by any government department or PSU as of the date of this undertaking.

Authorized Signatory
{{contractorName}}

We affirm that all information and documents provided for {{tenderTitle}} are true, correct, and complete. We understand that false statements may lead to rejection.

Authorized Signatory
{{contractorName}}

Contractor: {{contractorName}}
Contact: {{contactPerson}} | {{contactMobile}} | {{email}}
Registered Address: {{address}}
Core Expertise: ____________________
Year of Establishment: ____________
Key Licenses: _____________________

(Attach additional sheets if needed)

To,
{{deptName}}

Subject: Bank details for correspondence

Account Name: {{contractorName}}
Bank: ______________________
Branch & IFSC: ______________
Account Number: _____________

This is for tender-related communications only (no bid values enclosed).

Authorized Signatory
{{contractorName}}

We acknowledge the EMD/SD requirements of the tender {{tenderTitle}} and undertake to furnish the required security in the prescribed manner if awarded.

Authorized Signatory
{{contractorName}}
